missionEventData.data1: Without her starfighter screen the Lulsla is vulnerable to bombardment. One flight of Tie Bombers and one flight of Assault Gunboats will bombard the Lulsla and her escorts. After the ship has been crippled the Star Destroyer Hammer will jump in to finish the job. Good luck!
There's the Lulsa. She won't be able to escape this time.
Alpha group we need to take out those Corvettes before the main force can begin its run.
Well done the Corvettes have been destroyed.
We're launching the main attack force now.
Warning a Squadron of X-Wings is launching from the Lulsla.
This is the ISD Hammer. Hope you don't mind if we help finish the job.
Not at all Hammer. Welcome to the fight.
The Rebels are starting to evacuate the Lulsla
Alpha 1 there are still rebel fighters present. Destroy them!
Well done Alpha 1, you can continue to patrol the area or return to the Fogger.
Well done, the remaining fighters have been destroyed.
Alpha 1, join the attack against the Lulsla.
The first corvette has been destroyed.

missionEventData.data2: At the battle of Yavin Rebel terrorists, aided by spies and traitors within the Empire, struck a cowardly blow at the new symbol of Imperial power... The Death Star! Darth Vader brought swift justice to the Rebels by destroying their main base on Hoth. The pitiful remnants of the Alliance have now scattered to the Outer Rim. In the days ahead, the Emperor will call upon the Imperial Navy to eradicate the last vestiges of rebellion and restore law and order to the galaxy!
